<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4254.1.4>
    dc:creator "Batuwita, Sudesh; Udugampala, Sampath" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "Description of a new species of Cnemaspis (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Knuckles Range of Sri Lanka" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.545720>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.545721>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.545722> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.545720>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A, NMSL uncatalogued paratype of Cnemaspis kandambyi sp. nov. (flip vertically to show neck stripe); B, Cnemaspis kandambyi sp. nov., in life, not preserved from Meemure in the Matale District (courtesy of S. P. Benjamin) (Note the flattened tail and black stripe on neck with the NMSL uncatalogued paratype); C, Cnemaspis podihuna, topotype, WHT 7334, Maligawila in the Ampara District. Scale bar: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/545720/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.545721>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Cnemaspis kandambyi sp. nov., NMSL WHT 9466 (holotype), A, dorsal view of snout; B, precloacal and thigh regions showing arrangement of femoral and precloacal pores, and unpored scales. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/545721/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.545722>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Distribution of Cnemaspis kandambyi sp. nov. (triangles), C. molligodai (square) and C. podihuna (circles); locations of holotypes (in white); other locations (in black); Pallegama may represent by C. kandambyi sp. nov. (in gradient triangle). Distribution records of C. podihuna adopted from Karunaratna et al. (2011)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/545722/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

